**Edureka**
Edureka is an online education platform offering instructor-led courses in trending technologies like data science, AI, cloud computing, and programming.
It focuses on hands-on learning through live classes, real-world projects, and 24/7 support to help professionals upskill effectively.
With a global learner base across 100+ countries, it aims to make technical education accessible, practical, and career-oriented.

Link: https://www.edureka.co/

